aboutDescription: I am currently a sophomore majoring in Computer Science and intending to major in Data Science at UC Berkeley. So far, I have taken advantage of my education at UC Berkeley by taking courses like Data Structures, Efficient Algorithms, Machine Structures, Information Devices, Discrete Mathematics and Probability Theory. In the spring, I will be taking Machine Learning and Operation Systems and System Programming. In my free time, I like to play basketball, piano, workout, model, attend coding Hackathons, and remixing Electronic Dance Music.
